pages.name: How to make your first bagel
pages.body:
1. Gather ingredients: flour, water, yeast, salt, and oil.
2. Mix the dry ingredients together.
3. Add the wet ingredients and knead the dough.
4. Let the dough rise.
5. Shape the dough into bagels.
6. Bake the bagels.

pages.name: How to make your first cake
pages.body:
1. Gather ingredients: flour, sugar, eggs, butter, and baking powder.
2. Mix the dry ingredients together.
3. Add the wet ingredients and mix well.
4. Pour the batter into a greased cake pan.
5. Bake the cake.
